{"tid":1691391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【收皮啦分化撚失敗撚】大埔之外仲有元朗將軍澳！！","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:17.000Z","uid":110109,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3e19757ade0310dc1d4ac9c4c72b5a5054a20d","tid":1691391,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"根本就非常成功！！<br />\n一反19連登係咁話完喇完喇既分化風<br />\n<br />\n各區大把人仍然為公義肉緊<br />\n想贏、想救返義士<br />\n<br />\n又落撚曬柒頭港共既面<br />\n齋拎尋日黎講港共可以打飛機話暴力退潮<br />\n暴徒捉得7788<br />\n一日之後，各區商場都同你拆曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話驕兵<br />\n但係keep住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n老土講句<br />\n唔係因為有希望先至堅持！<br />\n而係因為堅持先有希望！！<br />\n光復香港、我地要贏返義士想要既香港<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\nbtw九龍東手足下禮拜好出黎！"},{"pid":"6826af03b46388e5aa76094930d22dfce858de09","tid":1691391,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6d497f9f468e9d94744f58df9ca3923a4729ec7","tid":1691391,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed09b9e1d464479a44cf7b8ad83024d57241fb0e","tid":1691391,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd9d85dda558978d1cb07f8ecc1182bd64e3a78","tid":1691391,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22966caecc0d6fc28b939b6a69459d55c7d34057","tid":1691391,"uid":201238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2942d9f7b12bbe37c277353a19bb44409975b2d4","tid":1691391,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,